  19 Feb 2020 - V3R1
     - Settings (Option 0)
       * Increased size of 'Status Interval' field to 3 characters,
         was 4 characters
     - User (Option 1)
       * When typing an 'S' next to a userid to show information,
         display the 'ATTRIButes' in the header of the panel, prior
         it displayed the 'DATA' field
